quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  21,11,"Ni imidugudu ingahe yakoraga ibikorwa bibi twarimbuye, maze nyuma yayo tukazana abandi bantu"
  21,12,"Nuko babonye ibihano byacu, bagerageza kwiruka babihunga"
  21,13,"(Babwirwa bannyegwa bati) “Mwihunga! Ahubwo nimusubire mu buzima bw’umunezero no mu ngo zanyu, kugira ngo mubazwe.”"
  21,14,Baravuga bati “Mbega ishyano tugushije! Mu by’ukuri twari inkozi z’ibibi.”
  21,15,"Ayo ni yo yakomeje kuba amaganya yabo, kugeza ubwo tubagize nk’imyaka yarandaguwe, ikuma"
  21,16,Ntabwo twaremye ikirere n’isi n’ibiri hagati yabyo dukina
  21,17,"Iyo tuza kuba dushaka ibitunezeza (kugira umwana cyangwa umugore), twari kubyitoranyiriza iwacu (mu ijuru, tutarinze kubikenera kuri mwe) iyo koko tuza kuba turi ababikora"
  21,18,"Ahubwo tugaragaza ukuri kugasenya ikinyoma, maze kikayoyoka. Kandi mufite akaga kubera ibyo mwitirira Allah (muvuga ko afite umugore n’umwana)"
  21,19,Abari mu birere no ku isi ni abe. Kandi abari iwe (abamalayika) ntibagira ubwibone ngo bumve ko batamusenga ndetse ntibananirwa
  21,20,Basingiza (Allah) ijoro n’amanywa ubutarambirwa
  21,21,Ese (ababangikanyamana) bishyiriyeho ibigirwamana bishobora kuzura (abapfuye) bibakuye mu butaka
  21,22,"Iyo (mu kirere no ku isi) haza kuba hari izindi mana zitari Allah, byombi byari kuba mu kaduruvayo. Ubutungane ni ubwa Allah, Nyagasani Nyiri Ar’shi ihambaye, nta ho ahuriye n’ibyo bamwitirira"
  21,23,"(Allah) ntabazwa ibyo akora, nyamara bo (ibiremwa) bazabazwa (ibyo bakora)"
  21,24,"Ese birakwiye ko (ababangikanyamana) bishyiriraho izindi mana zitari We? Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ngaho nimuzane ikimenyetso cyanyu (gihamya ukuri kw’ibyo musenga). Iyi (Qur’an) ni urwibutso ku bari kumwe nanjye (abemeramana), ikaba n’urwibutso ku babayeho mbere yanjye (kuko ibitabo byayibanjirije na byo byahakanye ko Imana ibangikanywa). Ariko abenshi muri bo ntibazi ukuri, ku bw’ibyo ntacyo bitaho.”"
  21,25,Kandi nta ntumwa twigeze twohereza mbere yawe (yewe Muhamadi) ngo tubure kuyihishurira ko nta yindi mana ibaho ikwiriye gusengwa mu kuri itari Njye (Allah). Bityo nimungaragire (njyenyine)
  21,26,Kandi (Ababangikanyamana) baravuze bati “(Allah) Nyirimpuhwe afite umwana. Ubutagatifu ni ubwe (ntibibaho ko yagira umwana)! Ahubwo (abo bamalayika bita abana be) ni abagaragu bubashywe.”
  21,27,"Nta cyo bajya bavuga batagitegetswe (na Allah), kandi bubahiriza itegeko rye"
  21,28,"(Abo bamalayika, Allah) azi ibiri imbere yabo n’inyuma yabo (ibyo bakoze n’ibyo bazakora), kandi ntibashobora kugira uwo bavuganira (Allah) atamwishimiye. Ndetse bahora bicishije bugufi kubera kumutinya"
  21,29,N’uwo ari we wese muri bo (abamalayika) wavuga ati “Mu by’ukuri njye ndi imana mu cyimbo cye (Allah)”; uwo twazamuhanisha umuriro wa Jahanamu. Kandi uko ni ko duhemba inkozi z’ibibi